{
  "specification": "1. Go to 'https://tubitv.com/'.\n    2. If a consent, cookie, or welcome dialog appears, dismiss it without signing in.\n    3. Click the magnifying-glass search icon in the top navigation to open the search overlay.\n    4. Type 'Lego' into the search textbox and press Enter.\n    5. Wait for the results grid to appear, then click the first title card.\n    6. Wait for the movie/show page to load, then click the Play button and wait <secret>watch_seconds</secret> seconds before stopping.",
